Sentimental		KEY:Sentimental ~ Drawback	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Sentimental ~ Drawback],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback]	DESC:You are sentimental, and your thoughts often stray to the past at inappropriate times.					COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.65	BENEFIT:You are sentimental, and your thoughts often stray to the past at inappropriate times. You take a -2 penalty on Perception checks to avoid being surprised and on Reflex saving throws to avoid traps or hazards.
Vain			KEY:Vain ~ Drawback		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Vain ~ Drawback],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback]		DESC:You are sensitive about the way others perceive you.											COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.65	BENEFIT:You are sensitive about the way others perceive you. Whenever you fail an opposed Charisma-based check, you take a -2 penalty on all Charisma-based checks for the next 24 hours.
Xenophobic		KEY:Xenophobic ~ Drawback	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Xenophobic ~ Drawback],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback]	DESC:You have a hard time understanding and trusting those with unfamiliar ways and appearances.				COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.65	BENEFIT:You have a hard time understanding and trusting those with unfamiliar ways and appearances. You take a -2 penalty on Diplomacy and Sense Motive checks made against creatures of a different race or from a different culture.
Zealous		KEY:Zealous ~ Drawback		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Zealous ~ Drawback],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback]		DESC:You are fanatical in your beliefs, ruled by emotion over reason.									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.65	BENEFIT:You are fanatical in your beliefs, ruled by emotion over reason. When you attack a creature that you know worships a different religion than you do, you take a -5 penalty on the attack  roll and a +2 trait bonus on the damage roll with your first attack.

